<h2 id="when-to-use-browser-check">When to use browser check</h2>

<p>Use browser check on all pages of the website to ensure that no matter what page a user lands on, they are encouraged to upgrade their browser to enhance their experience.</p>

<h2 id="how-to-use-browser-check">How to use browser check</h2>

<p>Browser check should be placed near the start of the <code>&lt;body&gt;</code> tag, directly after the <a href="/essex-service-transformation-playbook/Design-system/Elements-and-Components/skip-link">skip link</a> element.</p>
